quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  3,23,"Ese (yewe Muhamadi) ntiwamenye ba bandi bahawe ingabire (yo gusobanukirwa) Igitabo, bahamagarirwa kugana Igitabo cya Allah kugira ngo kibakiranure, maze bamwe muri bo bagatera umugongo bakanirengangiza"
  3,24,Ibyo babiterwa n’uko bavuze bati “Umuriro ntuzatugeraho uretse iminsi mbarwa.” Kandi boshywa n’ibyo bihimbiraga mu idini ryabo (ko bazababarirwa cyangwa bakaba mu muriro iminsi mike)
  3,25,"Bizamera bite nitubakusanyiriza hamwe ku munsi udashidikanywaho, maze buri muntu agahemberwa mu buryo bwuzuye ibyo yakoze? Kandi ntabwo bazahuguzwa"
  3,26,"Vuga uti “Nyagasani Mwami (Nyirubwami)! Ugabira ubwami uwo ushaka ukanyaga ubwami uwo ushaka. Wubahisha uwo ushaka ugasuzuguza uwo ushaka. Ibyiza biri mu kuboko kwawe. Mu by’ukuri, ni wowe Ushobora byose.”"
  3,27,"“Winjiza ijoro mu manywa, ukaninjiza amanywa mu ijoro. Ukura ikizima mu cyapfuye unakura icyapfuye mu kizima, kandi ugaha amafunguro uwo ushaka nta kugera.”"
  3,28,"Abemeramana ntibakagire abahakanyi inshuti ngo babarutishe abemera. Uzakora ibyo azaba yitandukanyije na Allah, keretse hari inabi mutinya ko yabaturukaho (icyo gihe ntimuzabereke urwango. Nimunavuga urukundo bizabe ari ku munwa bitari ku mutima). Allah arababurira kumutinya, kandi kwa Allah ni ho (byose) bizasubira"
  3,29,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Mwahisha ibiri mu bituza byanyu cyangwa mukabigaragaza, Allah arabimenya, akanamenya ibiri mu birere no mu isi.” Kandi Allah ni Ushobora byose"